  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to learn about the effect of Liraglutide, (Victoza®),
      on the fat surrounding the heart.Excessive amount of the fat around the heart is common in
      people with type 2 diabetes and can be associated with poor sugar control. Liraglutide is an
      injectable prescription medicine that can improve blood sugar control in adults with type 2
      diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
